Pertama, minumlah susu kunyit ini.

00:17:02.479 --> 00:17:03.509
Ayo.

00:17:04.394 --> 00:17:06.130
Ayolah..
- Tidak, Kakak Ipar.

00:17:06.937 --> 00:17:09.409
