00:17:11.048 --> 00:17:14.737
Entah Anda merasa lapar atau
tidak, tapi bayi mungkin saja lapar.

00:17:14.977 --> 00:17:16.615
Pokoknya bayinya pasti bosan

00:17:16.665 --> 00:17:19.443
mendengarkan ejekan kakek-bibi.

00:17:19.507 --> 00:17:21.793
Benar?  Ayo, selesaikan.
- Ipar..

00:17:22.115 --> 00:17:25.025
Kumohon.. Jangan paksa aku..
- Kakak Ipar!

00:17:25.080 --> 00:17:26.122
Anda..

